    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/483980/extras/a04099965f7fa0cd02f6511cc45d55d4.poster.avif?t=1735191803\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/483980/extras/a04099965f7fa0cd02f6511cc45d55d4.webm?t=1735191803\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/483980/extras/a04099965f7fa0cd02f6511cc45d55d4.mp4?t=1735191803\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/483980/extras/6e4ea44aa72679814e409b5cc5ac957f.avif?t=1735191803\" width=600 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《狂父》是由日本むぎせん玩家制作的恐怖解密类单机游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们可以操纵女主角阿雅(アヤ)，在大豪宅里阿雅去拯救爸爸途中会遇上各种难题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/483980/extras/12963d338d56f6cea35909a2c1fff78f.avif?t=1735191803\" width=600 height=80 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > 阿雅</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作的女主角。隐约知道父亲进行可怕实验但不肯面对现实的女孩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/483980/extras/e6b5aff517054b932dd337ef4c509900.avif?t=1735191803\" width=200 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >父亲</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >阿雅的父亲。在大豪宅的地下室内进行可怕的实验活动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/483980/extras/432cc793f9af4f0dea72916c117906f9.avif?t=1735191803\" width=200 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >母亲</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >阿雅的母亲。在游戏开始时的一年前就已经去世了，深爱着阿雅父亲，并且真相是……(在取得她写给阿雅的父亲情信中可以了解到)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/483980/extras/50df6c4f6f174547031a90ba6645c73c.avif?t=1735191803\" width=200 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > 玛莉亚</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以阿雅父亲的助手及情人的身分，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >居住在这个家里的女仆。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/483980/extras/17efaca569f392c8ad6ebfabe0ce3801.avif?t=1735191803\" width=200 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > 谜之黑衣人</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >经常在故事中突然出现并帮助阿雅，自称推销员。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集了所有宝石後在IF剧情中知道其真正目的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/483980/extras/a8282db64ffa257219b054ffde76417c.avif?t=1735191803\" width=200 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > 金髪的少年</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >协助阿雅离开大屋的谜之少年。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/483980/extras/27b1daf54eaf908b2f4e028c494a2537.avif?t=1735191803\" width=200 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/483980/extras/319ffd43e3c2611949d268548cf5937d.avif?t=1735191803\" width=600 height=80 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > 电锯</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可将木材等破坏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >暗号笔记</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据笔记的提示可打开密码锁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >宝石</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >重要物品。隐藏於大屋各处。如收集所有宝石的话……？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >结局</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >共有3个结局，其中一个为官方设定的真正结局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在完成结局後，再重新多玩一遍游戏，将会看到爸爸及妈妈所写的日记，以及妈妈写给爸爸的情信。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >僵尸</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >袭击阿雅的僵尸，是阿雅的父亲在实验中的亡魂。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请注意持有武器的僵尸，被捉住的话随时被杀。</p>",
